---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Pinglab</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="px-6 py-16 lg:pl-[15%] lg:pr-16">
      <div class="max-w-[46rem]">
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4">
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Pinglab</h1>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/eoinmurray/pinglab"
            class="text-sm text-[color:var(--muted)] hover:text-[color:var(--ink)]"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
          >github</a>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[color:var(--muted)]">
          Spiking neural networks with explicit E/I and PING dynamics.
        </p>

        <section class="mt-10 space-y-4 text-[color:var(--ink)]">
          <p>
            A PING network has explicit excitatory and inhibitory populations wired in a feedback
            loop that produces gamma rhythms. This site trains them on classification tasks and
            measures them against simpler recurrent baselines.
          </p>
          <p>
            The shared diagnostic is Δt-stability: train at one integration timestep, evaluate at
            another. Models grounded in continuous-time dynamics generalise across Δt; models that
            overfit their training step do not.
          </p>
          <p>
            Findings, method changes, and archived drafts all live in one
            <a href="/journal/">journal</a> — dated entries, newest first.
          </p>
        </section>

        <p class="mt-10 mb-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[color:var(--muted)]">Start here</p>
        <ul class="pl-0 list-none space-y-1">
          <li><a href="/motivation/">Motivation</a></li>
          <li><a href="/models/">Models</a></li>
          <li><a href="/journal/">Journal</a></li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-8 mb-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-[color:var(--muted)]">References</p>
        <ul class="pl-0 list-none space-y-1">
          <li><a href="/training/">Training</a></li>
          <li><a href="/metrics/">Metrics</a></li>
          <li><a href="/llm-context/">LLM Context</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
